{"tid":39860,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"上帝可唔可以創造出比賭博墮天錄更拖戲既漫畫","createTime":"2016-12-14T22:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T13:38:13.000Z","uid":26167,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8674020c05ae450adcff8c930aac9984181dfd42","tid":39860,"uid":26167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T22:16:10.000Z","msg":"利申左先小弟極少睇動漫，可能大驚小怪唔好屌我<br />\n人生基本上剩係睇過TVB播過果啲死亡筆記，鋼鍊，火影果啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早排上網無啦啦見到賭博默示錄，見到好似幾得意就睇下啦<br />\n諗住藤原龍也果套電影版都成7-8年前，<br />\n應該一早完晒好耐啦<br />\n一口氣睇完賭博默示錄，破戒錄，<br />\n岩岩好去到十五分鐘前睇晒墮天錄，<br />\n睇到195話覺得奇怪啦，明明故事都未完但係就無更新，<br />\n開司來回地獄又折返人間咁同和也五五波，<br />\n咁我就以為係個漫畫APP問題，起身用電腦search，<br />\n點知發現原來個漫畫仲係連載中，我已經覺得好出奇<br />\n<br />\n然後我發現，墮天錄分三part，<br />\n由開頭第一part對社長打麻雀，<br />\n第二part和也篇睇爆頭遊戲，<br />\n第三part單張撲克篇同和也賭poker，<br />\n呢三part係故事裡面係同一晚發生，<br />\n但我係check番wiki，<br />\n墮天錄開始連載既時候係2004年28號，<br />\n而第三part到依家2016年12月15日仲係連載中，<br />\n換句話講......<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">故事裡面既一晚現實畫撚左12年，係12年呀！！！<br />\n仲要係未撚完架！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老味姐係由我小學四年級，仲學緊分數乘除，<br />\n變到依家year 4就黎grad啦屌你老母！！！！！<br />\n而都係未完，係仲未完架！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思可能係我大驚小怪，但我想講我呢刻既心情真係好複雜，<br />\n我好想知，究竟會係我死先定係開司死先，<br />\n如果我死左，希望有巴打可以燒呢套漫畫既結局比我"},{"pid":"1532585c3fa8f1364beef58365d652a31fe4fb7c","tid":39860,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T22:17:04.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"6e7a7661acda309c7f868d930ceb21e07e2a4a80","tid":39860,"uid":26937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T22:27:10.000Z","msg":"烙印戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28383528face3780fa7bcc354bd66a20bcf7a43f","tid":39860,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:24:18.000Z","msg":"但一開頭係幾好睇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 至少去到和也篇之前"},{"pid":"15a5ea59241ee953d423fbdf4ba67b85410d2615","tid":39860,"uid":63160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:32:14.000Z","msg":"HQ 加插勁多無謂劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b396b0357a7f666235c2d48c04b632eddb037435","tid":39860,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:33:56.000Z","msg":"佢好似同時仲連載緊其他漫畫"},{"pid":"50e671c850bb70b9a360f6b7346e988432624799","tid":39860,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:34:03.000Z","msg":"你可以睇之前個一部<br />\n個部就完咗"},{"pid":"5d0c23ba5dd3dbaaa4f307fff5eb0ae675476b58","tid":39860,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:36:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>烙印戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhxh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81208b219b75f18929c93cf7d4734fc051b5c994","tid":39860,"uid":19141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:44:40.000Z","msg":"你睇埋佢另一套鬥牌傳說先再講啦<br />\n套野講打麻雀既<br />\n好記得有一話講個敵人抽到張好牌<br />\n之後就話畫一大堆野講乜神助運氣返黎啦<br />\n咁就完左一集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果局打左最小有十年既麻雀<br />\n到e家都唔知打完未<br />\n<br />\n另外佢果套銀與金我覺得好正<br />\n我睇果陣漢化開始左無耐我<br />\n追實個不定期更新既追度<br />\n果陣追都覺得無乜點拖戲<br />\n而且我小數我真係會期待睇下集既漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c12760a81af169a4cb96bb330b4b3c8e323a37","tid":39860,"uid":37992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T23:48:37.000Z","msg":"龍狼傳拖撚左廿年有多都未完添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本大把作者食緊老本唔諗住畫完佢"},{"pid":"2b8d6db9644c3e57cd3bfccc257ad6959de58729","tid":39860,"uid":33806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:10:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍狼傳拖撚左廿年有多都未完添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本大把作者食緊老本唔諗住畫完佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個問題唔係拖<br />\n拖就大把人拖啦<br />\n而係福本將極短時間之內發生既事無限延長"},{"pid":"a097aaa3b5fdd859a0c5ef4829b10647be8dc379","tid":39860,"uid":26167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:13:14.000Z","msg":"聽過好多動漫會拖，<br />\n我只係震撼在，<br />\n故事入面既一晚等於現實十二年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0e263b3882444ae37fed0548c177a7c9b81953","tid":39860,"uid":35814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:15:19.000Z","msg":"給開司一鑵啤酒先啦"},{"pid":"fc79b8e33f7dbbc04c816da2617a06f9e745e3e3","tid":39860,"uid":37866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:18:06.000Z","msg":"呢套真係拖到仆街<br />\n抽一張牌都畫三話"},{"pid":"f541bfbd42571462fa01d8581a95e623bd892473","tid":39860,"uid":2752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>給開司一鑵啤酒先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只要5000貝利卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7940530c2f5c31048612591bbd8e8c7667447e0f","tid":39860,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:50:56.000Z","msg":"老實，佢到彈珠台都幾好睇<br />\n打麻雀都有少少悶<br />\n到爆頭遊戲個到，我悶得滯飛左十幾話<br />\n個三條粉腸都係無穿無爛無追展過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係個十幾話唔睇係無乜影響"},{"pid":"e1de14238d5094b39350e0752c146436aec560ab","tid":39860,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:05:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>烙印戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套我原諒佢 話晒佢只係興趣使然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819cd987313af99a3b8e4bad814807a134775d40","tid":39860,"uid":62467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>烙印戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhxh<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n富奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b9425acb1a2c03a7986605ca09dabeff0abff2","tid":39860,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>烙印戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢套我原諒佢 話晒佢只係興趣使然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢套越畫越高質，但我驚佢死都未畫完<br />\n而家得閒諗起格里菲斯都嬲嬲地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賭博真係痴線，開一張牌用十幾廿集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經變成左呃稿費機器<br />\n<br />\n仲有彼岸島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47274ca2e65ec17e6468d503a767edcb2471f9e7","tid":39860,"uid":48947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:12:33.000Z","msg":"依套野真係戇鳩到極<br />\n拖劇情<br />\n畫風差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5dcc29fa014c435f2d7010e62f5ccb3918dc37","tid":39860,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:14:12.000Z","msg":"鬥牌傳說<br />\n打麻雀打左十幾年"},{"pid":"4e44b27aae7f4f8f222be9d1149806db53108d06","tid":39860,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你睇埋佢另一套鬥牌傳說先再講啦<br />\n套野講打麻雀既<br />\n好記得有一話講個敵人抽到張好牌<br />\n之後就話畫一大堆野講乜神助運氣返黎啦<br />\n咁就完左一集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果局打左最小有十年既麻雀<br />\n到e家都唔知打完未<br />\n<br />\n另外佢果套銀與金我覺得好正<br />\n我睇果陣漢化開始左無耐我<br />\n追實個不定期更新既追度<br />\n果陣追都覺得無乜點拖戲<br />\n而且我小數我真係會期待睇下集既漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未完"},{"pid":"ce70b431ab2af37ca40587c7e407ac0549ee015b","tid":39860,"uid":34275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:16:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>烙印戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多成四十年先去到妖精島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟手又停左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9da31ec2757717c206c776df5476dd61d7f49ff","tid":39860,"uid":39441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"講拖一定係彼岸島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一期得十版但係用三版講返上果期<br />\n睇過就明<br />\n<br />\n上面講果d咩 hxh係劇情上無拖<br />\n係拖稿姐"},{"pid":"119a44330a2df3a92f19bbdcc6e567511ed4c1af","tid":39860,"uid":39441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>烙印戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n差唔多成四十年先去到妖精島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟手又停左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當完左啦我<br />\n加新元素同隊友果刻佢已經玩大左<br />\n收唔到田尾"}]}